  "source_notes": "Sy Scholfield quotes him on Twitter, \"Nothing like a Mother’s Love My Beautiful  Elaine Chaney who carried me for 9 months August 2 1981…..8am I’ll be 41 in a couple hours & I just wanted to see My parents before I hit the road on this press run. I was able to cut my phone off & get some rest & enjoy my Parents.\" (The birthday post also includes a video of him with his mother, with his mother stating, \"I think it was like eight o'clock in the morning,\" after he asks, \"Ma, what time was I born on August 2nd... 1981\" [https://twitter.com/traychaney/status/1554275059090563072]. He has tweeted many times that his home town is \"Forestville MD/Washington DC.\"\\n",
